51f81bb3a90e3b38e3580ad856f9248a3407b161eb57730b1ae049b014c7247af2d38f162553437934e8b357303a8b2b92dad5a62854f3145d57ff898d733c5f  TestHTTPClientSanitizeJSONControlCharactersC0.patch
57be81e57c0bb5c36e07b6ff2aab661f1a9cd0bbab3ef159c24d59098451858c44fce09d2f5eb86380044568a6acc46ed65b56a87f5a3dc4057d5579e8f420aa  no-ignore-goflags.patch
"
